alysis\",\"prompt\":\"You are a senior security engineer. Analyze these code changes for security vulnerabilities. Focus on HIGH-CONFIDENCE issues (>80% exploitability). Skip DoS, rate limiting, secrets-on-disk, and theoretical issues.\\n\\n## CODE CHANGES\\n\\n### app/api/qa/route.ts (NEW FILE)\\n```typescript\\nimport { NextRequest, NextResponse } from 'next/serveâ€¦","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","subtitle":"{\"description\":\"Security vulnerability analysis\",\"prompt\":\"You are a senior security engineer. Analyze these code changâ€¦","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:47:13.894Z","title":"Agent","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqwsvw29_bba900cd756c":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_bba900cd756c","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01WcPEFRaHRggqTgED4dCGh5\"} | [{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I now have everything needed for a complete analysis. Here are the findings.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Security Review Findings\\n\\n### FINDING 1 â€” Data Exposure via `SELECT *` on `users` table\\n\\n**File:** `/Users/gwang/Develop/noteboard/lib/auth.ts`, line 32-38 (pre-existing, but newly triggered by QA routes)\\n\\n**Severity:** HIGH\\n**Caâ€¦","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01WcPEFRaHRggqTgED4dCGh5\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:47:59.249Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvw29_a8d3a2567611":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_a8d3a2567611","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"description\":\"FP filter: structural password_hash exposure\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security false-positive filter. Assess whether this finding is a real vulnerability or a false positive.\\n\\n## FINDING\\n**Category:** Data Exposure (structural)\\n**File:** `lib/auth.ts` line 32\\n**Confidence claimed:** 9/10\\n\\n`getSessionUser()` does `SELECT u.* FROM users u JOIN sessions` â€” returns full User objectâ€¦","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","subtitle":"{\"description\":\"FP filter: structural password_hash exposure\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security false-positive filter. Assesâ€¦","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:48:19.728Z","title":"Agent","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqwsvw29_e609c3b91418":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_e609c3b91418","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"description\":\"FP filter: IDOR TOCTOU re-fetch\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security false-positive filter. Assess whether this finding is a real vulnerability or a false positive.\\n\\n## FINDING\\n**Category:** IDOR / TOCTOU re-fetch\\n**File:** `app/api/qa/[id]/route.ts` line 70\\n**Confidence claimed:** 8/10\\n\\nThe PUT handler:\\n1. Runs `UPDATE qa_items SET ... WHERE id = ? AND user_id = ?` â€” ownership vâ€¦","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","subtitle":"{\"description\":\"FP filter: IDOR TOCTOU re-fetch\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security false-positive filter. Assess whether thiâ€¦","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:48:28.548Z","title":"Agent","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqwsvw29_40401c409dfb":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_40401c409dfb","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_012YijbTcPgv7sjwSp1ACAuc\"} | [{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"CONFIDENCE_SCORE: 2\\n\\n**Reasoning:**\\n\\nThis is a false positive by the criteria provided.\\n\\nThe finding explicitly acknowledges that the actual QA routes do NOT return the user object â€” the handler returns `qa_items` rows from separate SELECT queries. The security reviewer's own description frames this as a \\\"latent\\\" risâ€¦","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_012YijbTcPgv7sjwSp1ACAuc\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:48:31.980Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvw29_c38220093bae":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_c38220093bae","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01XwSYhivxYiX2ppLEDm2wof\"} | [{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"CONFIDENCE_SCORE: 2/10\\n\\n**False positive.**\\n\\nThe claimed attack path requires a deleted row's ID to be reassigned to a different user's row between the UPDATE and the re-fetch SELECT. That is impossible here for two compounding reasons:\\n\\n1. **SQLite AUTOINCREMENT prevents ID reuse entirely.** The `sqlite_sequence` tablâ€¦","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01XwSYhivxYiX2ppLEDm2wof\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:48:35.628Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvw29_12f13cdf024f":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_12f13cdf024f","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:48:46.588Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvw29_2cd84907d04a":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_2cd84907d04a","importance":5,"narrative":"<command-message>security-review</command-message>\n<command-name>/security-review</command-name>","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:50:19.045Z","title":"prompt_submit","type":"conversation"},"obs_mqwsvw29_435235da9c1b":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvw29_435235da9c1b","importance":5,"narrative":"You are a senior security engineer conducting a focused security review of the changes on this branch.\n\nGIT STATUS:\n\n```\nOn branch superspec\nYour branch is up to date with 'origin/superspec'.\n\nChanges not staged for commit:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to update what will be committed)\n  (use \"git restore <file>...\" to discard changes in working directory)\n\tmodified:   .claude/settings.json\n\tmodifiâ€¦","sessionId":"deab992a-a996-4496-bc13-161a5a273e6a","timestamp":"2026-06-17T14:50:19.045Z","title":"prompt_submit","type":"conversation"},"obs_mqwsvw29_bd172801919f":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"f